title: DDFP 465: Best WR Groups & 2nd Best All-Time NFL Player
itunes:title: DDFP 465: Best WR Groups & 2nd Best All-Time NFL Player
description:
Shek is joined by Dan Hanzus & Patrick Claybon to discuss the top wide receiver groups going into 2016 and the best comebacks in all of sports.  The guys also name their 2nd best NFL players of all time, as well as the best television and film dads.  Plus, the guys compete in another surprise game show and wrap with a chat about the most recent episode of “Game of Thrones.”
